{
  "stem": "20609.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had no-- at the school I was, we had no-- we had a very small gymnasium, and, you know, we had no place to play.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had no-- no place to play soccer or anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we were at that time already very closed in, you know, till November when the famous Crystal Night started, when they-- when they burned down our synagogue and our-- our school was right at the same place.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I remember I came-- I went with my friend over-- I met my friend at the school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We saw the school burning and were sort of a little happy there for a while.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, I said, my god, we don't have to get up in the morning anymore, right?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that didn't last too long because then you started realizing what are you going to do?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so he asked me, he said, let's go over to see-- go over to my father's store.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He's got-- he's cleaning up all the windows were broken.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We help him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, why not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was 8 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Where was I going to go?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we went over the-- his father's store.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We helped him cleaning up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we saw that big mob coming towards the store.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the-- the father locked himself and ourselves into the repair shop, which, thank god, had a metal door.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But there was no other way to get out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only way you can get out-- go back to the store.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were locked in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were locked in about six or seven hours.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We heard the people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who has size eight?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were handing out school-- shoes to everybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
